{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"languagechange","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/languagechange_event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>这是一个实验中的功能</strong><br>此功能某些浏览器尚在开发中，请参考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">浏览器兼容性表格</a>以得到在不同浏览器中适合使用的前缀。由于该功能对应的标准文档可能被重新修订，所以在未来版本的浏览器中该功能的语法和行为可能随之改变。</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p>当用户首选语言更改时，将在全局范围对象上触发 languagechange 事件。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"general_info","title":"General info","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"specification\">Specification</dt>\n <dd><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/indices.html#event-languagechange\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"HTML Living Standard\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard</a></dd>\n <dt id=\"interface\">Interface</dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></dd>\n <dt id=\"bubbles\">Bubbles</dt>\n <dd>No</dd>\n <dt id=\"cancelable\">Cancelable</dt>\n <dd>No</dd>\n <dt id=\"target\">Target</dt>\n <dd>The default window scope, being <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a> on Web pages and <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a> in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API/Using_web_workers\">Web Workers</a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"default_action\">Default Action</dt>\n <dd>None</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Being of type <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a>, this event implements the properties of this interface.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"event.target\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event/target\"><code>Event.target</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns an <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a> that is the topmost target in the DOM tree of the event.</dd>\n <dt id=\"event.type\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event/type\"><code>Event.type</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a> representing the type of event, here <code>\"languagechange\"</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"event.bubbles\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event/bubbles\"><code>Event.bubbles</code></a><span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> indicating if the event normally bubbles or not.</dd>\n <dt id=\"event.cancelable\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event/cancelable\"><code>Event.cancelable</code></a><span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> indicating if it is possible to cancel the event.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specification","id":"specification","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/indices.html#event-languagechange","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.Window.languagechange_event"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Window.languagechange_event","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/languagechange_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/language\"><code>navigator.language</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/languages\"><code>navigator.languages</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/languagechange_event\"><code>Window.onlanguagechange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"General info","id":"general_info"},{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Specification","id":"specification"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"当用户首选语言更改时，将在全局范围对象上触发 languagechange 事件。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window: languagechange event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Window: languagechange event","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Window: languagechange イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/window/languagechange_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/window/languagechange_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window","title":"Window"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/languagechange_event","title":"languagechange"}],"pageTitle":"languagechange - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}